/**
 * \page BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation Signal Stream Concatenation
__________________________________________________________________

Detailed description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Description|
 The input streams must share the same characteristics : sampling frequency, number of channels, sample count per block.
 User can specify a time-out value beyond which a stream is considered as finished if no samples are received.
 If user wants a specific part of a given stream, he can specify a stimulation used as end-of-stream trigger.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Description|
__________________________________________________________________

Inputs description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Inputs|
 The box has a pair of input (signal, stimulation) per source.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Inputs|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Input1|
 Signal stream from source #1.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Input1|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Input2|
 Stimulation stream from source #1.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Input2|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Input3|
 Signal stream from source #2.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Input3|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Input4|
 Stimulation stream from source #2.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Input4|
__________________________________________________________________

Outputs description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Outputs|
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Outputs|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Output1|
 Concatenated signal stream.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Output1|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Output2|
 Concatenated stimulation stream.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Output2|
__________________________________________________________________

Settings description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Settings|
 A stimulation setting is added for each input pair.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Settings|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Setting1|
 If no samples are received beyond this time-out value, a stream is considered as finished.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Setting1|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Setting2|
 Stimulation that triggers the end-of-stream for source #1.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Setting2|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Setting3|
 Stimulation that triggers the end-of-stream for source #2.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Setting3|
__________________________________________________________________

Examples description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Examples|
 This box is mainly designed to concatenate multiple signal files.
 For example, you have 10 sessions of training and you want to train a classifier on the whole set of data.
 You can use the Signal Stream Concatenation to produce one EEG file containing the 10 sessions, 
 and then feed a \ref Doc_BoxAlgorithm_ClassifierTrainer box with it.
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Examples|
__________________________________________________________________

Miscellaneous description
__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Miscellaneous|
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_SignalStreamConcatenation_Miscellaneous|
 */
